     </div>

    <div class="attribute-byline">
	    </div>

    

    <div class="attribute-body float-break">
      <p>While eZ Publish is&nbsp;totally&nbsp;well fitted to store and deliver great video experiences, there are cases where you might want to do more than what the eZ Platform can offer. There are cases where you might want to benefit from cutting edge digital video capabilities without the hassle of operating it on your eZ Publish installation. In this cases, the only way to go is to integrate with a cloud video platform such as the Brightcove platform. eZ Publish Platform being open and extensible by design, Kaliop was able to design an extension that is very seamlessly integrated in eZ Publish and very simple to use.</p>
