        <h1><a href="/Mirror/eZ-Systems-News">eZ Systems News</a></h1>
     </div>
    <div class="attribute-header">
        <h2>> <a href="http://ez.no/About-eZ/Events-News/News/eZ-Live-Viewer-2-unveils-new-simple-to-use-real-time-web-analytics-solution-for-content-rich-websites" title="eZ Live Viewer 2 unveils new simple to use real-time web analytics solution for content rich websites">eZ Live Viewer 2 unveils new simple to use real-time web analytics ...</a></h2>
     </div>

    <div class="attribute-byline">
	    </div>

    

    <div class="attribute-body float-break">
      <p>While version 1.0 of eZ Live Viewer focused on providing a real-time content trending solution, this new version offers many new features to benefit organizations dealing with large volumes of content and with high levels of web traffic.</p><p>The vision behind eZ Live Viewer is to create an analytics tool that is so easy to use and interpret that non-technical staff can work on it straight away. Intuitive insights via a unique infographic visualization has been the driver to enable a large range of users to work with this analytics solution straight away. Additionally today’s analytics tools must focus on real-time analysis, as very few businesses can afford the luxury of waiting for the data to be captured, processed, analyzed and digested.</p><p>“Ultimately, the tool should release you from needing to hire a data scientist to understand a lot of what is going on on your website and be able to react quickly. Getting easy to use analytics into the hands of content managers and editors is a major efficiency driver,” says Roland Benedetti, VP Product Services.</p><p>“It is very exciting to reach now a stage where we are able to provide predictive analytics that are understandable and concrete when it comes to improving the performance of websites” says Christof Zahneissen, Chief Product Officer at eZ Systems. “For instance, we are able to recommend changes to front pages, and predict a measurable gain on the recommendation, like ‘your conversion rate will be improved by 12.5%’”. &nbsp;This is a new step forward in the direction of providing a global experience management platform.</p>
<div class=""><div class="content-view-embed">
	<div class="class-image">
		<div class="attribute-image">

	
															
		
		
																								
													
													
						
			<a href="http://ez.no/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/media/images/front-page-monitor2/358441-1-eng-GB/Front-page-monitor_fancybox.png" rel="fancybox" class="fancybox"><img src="http://ez.no/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/media/images/front-page-monitor2/358441-1-eng-GB/Front-page-monitor_imagelarge.png" width="550" height="255" style="border: 0px solid ;" alt="The front page monitor" title="The front page monitor" /><span title="Enlarge this image"></span></a>		
		
		
	</div>
			</div>
</div>
</div><p><i>The Front Page Monitor</i></p><a name="eztoc358413_0_1" id="eztoc358413_0_1"></a><h3>Front Page Monitoring and Optimization</h3><p>Among the new features provided by eZ Live Viewer 2, the front-page monitoring is certainly the most important one. It continuously measures the performance of your front-page and recommends changes that will directly improve your conversion and engagement rate. For marketing and commerce oriented sites this can be measured in direct revenue gains; for publishers it increases traffic, boosts reader engagement and advertising revenue, for service related sites it improves content relevance and efficiency. This tool is not about simply measuring page views but really about analyzing in detail how the front-page and the content being pushed on it behaves and delivers.</p>
<div class=""><div class="content-view-embed">
	<div class="class-image">
		<div class="attribute-image">

	
															
		
		
																								
													
													
						
			<a href="http://ez.no/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/media/images/front-page-rearrangement-suggestions2/358445-1-eng-GB/Front-page-rearrangement-suggestions_fancybox.png" rel="fancybox" class="fancybox"><img src="http://ez.no/var/ezflow_site/storage/images/media/images/front-page-rearrangement-suggestions2/358445-1-eng-GB/Front-page-rearrangement-suggestions_imagelarge.png" width="550" height="255" style="border: 0px solid ;" alt="The front page recommendation" title="The front page recommendation" /><span title="Enlarge this image"></span></a>		
		
		
	</div>
			</div>
</div>
</div><p><i>And the front page recommendation</i></p><a name="eztoc358413_0_2" id="eztoc358413_0_2"></a><h3>Made for tablets as much as for large screen</h3><p>Because it’s developed with HTML5 technology and responsive design, eZ Live Viewer 2 has been designed to be used on tablets as much as on wide TV screens with the same unique user experience. From the CEO on the go on his iPad to the editor in the newsroom via TV screen or the marketeer directly on his computer, eZ Live Viewer provides the immediate and detailed pulse of what is going on on your website on all devices.</p><a name="eztoc358413_0_3" id="eztoc358413_0_3"></a><h3>Unique visualization concept for Content trending</h3><p>One of the major strengths of the initial eZ Live Viewer version was the visualization concept of traffic analysis and its graphic representation. eZ Live Viewer has been further improved in version 2.0 offering at a glance a sharp understanding of the activity on your website, from where the visitors come from to how they leave, and of course most importantly how they consume content whilst on your site.</p><a name="eztoc358413_0_4" id="eztoc358413_0_4"></a><h3>Availability</h3><p>Made for sites with big content and large traffic, eZ Live Viewer 2 is available as part of the eZ Publish Platform, integrated in the back office editorial suite, and can also be used as a standalone solution. It is delivered only as a service and is immediately available for existing and new customers.</p><p>Organizations interested in the solution and willing to try it are invited to register for a trial access on their site.</p><p>For more information, visit <a href="http://www.ez.no/market/ezliveviewer" target="_self">www.ez.no/market/ezliveviewer</a></p><a name="eztoc358413_0_5" id="eztoc358413_0_5"></a><h3>About eZ</h3><p>eZ Systems is the globally recognised commercial open source software provider. Our leading and innovative approach takes your enterprise platform beyond content management (CMS) into creating a true digital experience with systematic optimization capabilities. The eZ Publish platform sets new standards for digital lifecycle management, including recommendations and smart web analytics functionality, coupled with an application market place of certified extensions. Thousands of organizations worldwide benefit from optimized and intelligent multi-channel communications solutions. eZ's client base includes small, medium and large enterprises across all industries such as media, publishing and broadcasting, financial services, telecoms, retail, government, manufacturing, logistics, and education.</p>
    </div>

